                                        <li><strong>Know what your goals are </strong>
                                    </div>
                                    <br>Before you even begin creating a stock portfolio, it is extremely essential to first identify your goals. This way, you will be in a better position to create one that’s perfect for you. Although your ultimate goal
                                    is to generate returns, you would have to identify other aspects such as the time frame within which you expect your goals to be satisfied and the amount of money that you’re willing to invest.
                                    </li>
                                </div>
